Reclusa::

She looked at Perceptor. "I must say. I am impressed. I am sure you
had some hand in it's designs. Please, give me the guided tour."  She
took a few steps and stopped. "I would also like to hear more of your
specialties. After all, I know that your leader wouldn't have sent any
less than one of his best for me. So I know that you are a master in
your field. So, when I get settled in, you would tell me more of
yourself and this base. After all, how can any member of an effective
team function to thier highest capacity if they don't even know thier
own, eh, backyard, so to speak?"
